OL,3,CResidents allowed to return home after
OL,4,Cevacuation due to suspect package
OL,6,FPeople living on two streets in
OL,7,FLlanelli have been allowed to return
OL,8,Fhome after their properties were
OL,9,Fevacuated following the discovery of a
OL,10,F'suspect package.'
OL,12,FAn explosive ordnance disposal team
OL,13,Ffrom Dyfed Powys Police attended the
OL,14,Fincident on Long Row, Felinfoel, after
OL,15,Fan item was discovered just after
OL,16,Fmidday on Saturday 16 May.
OL,18,FA cordon was in place closing the road
OL,19,Fas well nearby Adulam Road with
OL,20,Fresidents on both streets being told
OL,21,Fto evacuate their houses.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/3
