OL,3,CResidents allowed to return home after
OL,4,Cevacuation due to suspect package
OL,6,FThe force along with Mid and West
OL,7,FWales Fire and Rescue Service and the
OL,8,FWelsh Ambulance Service, were
OL,9,Fdispatched to the scene.
OL,11,FIn an update on social media Dyfed
OL,12,FPowys Police said the item had been
OL,13,Fexamined at and confirmed "there is no
OL,14,Frisk to the public."
OL,16,FThey added, "the cordon and road
OL,17,Fclosures have now been lifted, and
OL,18,Fresidents who were evacuated can
OL,19,Freturn home.
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G2/3
