PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F461A1778965867
OL,3,CResidents allowed to return home after
OL,4,Cevacuation due to suspect package
OL,6,F"We recognise the inconvenience this
OL,7,Fhas caused, and thank you for your
OL,8,Fcooperation and patience while we
OL,9,Fensured your safety.
OL,11,F"Further enquiries will be carried out
OL,12,Fto establish the source of the item
OL,13,Fand the intention behind it being
OL,14,Fplaced in a public location."
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G3/3
